name: J. V. Lena Schulze
tagline: Exploring the wiring of your brain
body:
### Geek + Engineer + Neuroscientist 

![](/images/IMG_0147.JPG)

Lena spends most of her time doing research as a Phd student in the area of neural computation and machine learning at the Okinawa Institute of Science and Technology, Japan. 

In her spare time she develops iOS games in swift, paints, travels Asia, drinks a lot of coffee and cuddles with her cat Pankeki.
